meaning_str.bing:
n. 脚(=12英寸,1/3码,0.3048米)英尺；脚步
v. 付(款)；踏在…上；跳(舞)；给(袜子等)换底
网络. 足；双脚；脚部

付(款)；踏在…上；跳(舞)；给(袜子等)换底

脚；足；步态；韵脚；底部；立足点；支撑物；英尺（长度单位）；（foot的复数）

1.en: But it took all her strength just to get back to her feet, and when she did all she could do was stand there, fevered and bleeding.
1.cn: 可她使尽了全力才勉强站住脚，而好不容易站住之后却怎么也动不了，浑身发烫，血流不止。

2.en: As members of Christ's body, we are his hands, his feet, his eyes, and his heart. He works through us in the world.
2.cn: 作为基督身体的成员，我们是他的手、他的脚、他的眼，他的心，他透过我们在世上做工。

3.en: Then the Spirit came into me and raised me to my feet. He spoke to me and said: "Go, shut yourself inside your house. "
3.cn: 灵就进入我里面，使我站起来。耶和华对我说，你进房屋去，将门关上。

0.en: Our feet are touching. You're doing that.
0.cn: 咱俩的脚碰到一起了。还不是你伸过来了。

1.en: I wish I had shoes like that. My feet hurt.
1.cn: 我希望能有一双这样的鞋子，其实我的脚很痛。

2.en: The carpet smelled. Like ocean? No, like feet.
2.cn: 那间房的地毯有味道。大海的味道？是脚臭味。

3.cn: 拥有那样双脚的女人让人垂涎。

4.cn: 这和脚没有一毛钱关系。

5.en: I thought it has to do with the size of a guy's feet.
5.cn: 我认为那东西跟自己脚的大小相等。

6.en: Why don't you put just one foot into the water? Maybe you should try the other foot. Maybe George should try both feet at the same time. Good idea.
6.cn: 试试看，把一只脚放进水里？或许该试试另一只脚，或许应该把两只脚一起放进水里。这是个好主意！

7.en: You're gonna do some feet flirting. I don't what your talking about.
7.cn: 你要用脚勾引他。我不知道你们在说什么。

8.en: And then I can just walk over here and casually just put my feet right up on....
8.cn: 我可以走到这边，轻松的把脚翘在…

9.en: Emperor Yu believed that a woman's feet were the very essence of feminine beauty.
9.cn: 在李煜看来，女人的脚是女性之美的精华所在。

10.en: This is why he liked Yao Niang. Her feet were small, delicate, perfect.
10.cn: 所以他才喜欢窅娘，就因为她的脚小巧精致，堪称完美。

11.en: Measures had to be taken to keep their feet the perfect size. Three inches long.
11.cn: 必须采取一定措施才能让脚的尺寸保持完美，三寸之长。

12.en: Now you can come with us. Yeah, there's room in the bed by Sheldon's feet.
12.cn: 现在你可以跟我们一起住了。对啊，谢尔顿脚边还有地方睡哦。

13.en: What would happen to an astronaut daring or crazy enough to dive in feet-first?
13.cn: 对于一位足够勇敢或疯狂的宇航员脚先着地潜入会发生什么?

14.en: Oh Pheebs, is that a new ankle bracelet? Wow. And you got a pedicure. Your feet are all dressed up.
14.cn: 菲比，那是新脚链吗？你去修过脚趾甲。你的脚打扮过。

15.en: Okay. Now you can look. I love them! Where are my feet? They're still there! Okay.
15.cn: 好了 你可以看了。我爱它们! 我的脚呢? 还在这儿啊! 好吧。

16.en: All right, this is making me crazy. Somebody's got to go over there. You got feet and legs, you do it.
16.cn: 好了，我快疯了。你们谁过去一下。你有腿有脚，你去啊。

17.en: Of course if my feet are gonna be exposed, I'll need to update my tetanus booster. Oh, yeah. Makes sense.
17.cn: 当然了，如果我的脚要暴露在外，我就得去打新的破伤风疫苗。

18.en: Did you know that, per our roommate agreement, I have to wash my feet before I get in the shower?
18.cn: 你们知道吗，我们的室友协议里面规定，我必须在洗澡前先把脚洗干净？

19.en: So? You guys are all sleep deprived. I don't see you weeping because you put your slippers on the wrong feet. Oh God.
19.cn: 你们都会失眠，我没看过你因为鞋子穿错脚就哭个不停天啊。
